data.name: checkBox_nofsopt.ToolTip
data.value: Disables Windows 10/11 fullscreen optimizations, which can cause issues with screenshots and/or framerate.

data.name: label_Update_1.Text
data.value: Update PD Loader regularly to get the latest fixes and new features!

data.name: label_Update_2.Text
data.value: It is highly recommended to download updates directly from the official repository. If you have downloaded PD Loader from a third-party, it is recommended to do a clean installation.
